channel.title: Which euclidian sequencer do you use?
channel.description: Hi, I’m kind of new and got a bit lost with all the euclidean sequencer/generators available in the patcher. i don’t get to make some of them work, and other are doing some really weird stuff that I didn't really expected. I would be interested to know which one you like the most. All best, Olivier
